title: Anakin Skywalker, Tested By The Jedi Council
lore: Once each turn. when he draws destiny for a Battle card. a weapon, or his own power, you may discard that card and redraw.

title: Captain Panaka, Royal Defender
lore: He is considered to be a Naboo Officer, Royal Guard, and Naboo Security for all your cards.

title: Obi-Wan Kenobi, Jedi Avenger
lore: Adds 2 to the DAMAGE of each character he defeats.

title: Padmé Naberrie, Loyal Handmaiden
lore: Adds power bonus when Queen Amidala or any handmaiden has fought this turn.

title: R2-D2, Starship Maintenance Droid
lore: Adds power bonus to Amidala's Starship when that starship is evacuating this planet

title: Yoda, Wise Jedi
lore: Adds power bonus when your opponent has controlled a planet.

title: Aurra Sing, Scoundrel
lore: When she deploys, you may deploy Aurra Sing’s Blaster Rifle form your draw deck.

title: Darth Sidious, The Phantom Menace
lore: When he deploys to Coruscant, your opponent takes 2 DAMAGE.

title: Jabba The Hutt
lore: Adds power bonus when you have controlled Tatooine

title: Nute Gunray, Neimoidean Bureaucrat
lore: When he deploys to Naboo, you may deploy Rune Haaka from your draw deck.

title: Rune Haako, Neimoidean Lieutenant
lore: When he deploys to Naboo, you may deploy one Neimoidian from your draw deck.

title: Watto, Risk Taker
lore: Each time he draws destiny for a Battle card or weapon, draw two and choose one.Put both cards in your hand.
